{"id": "art-1531", "label": "Art. 1531", "title": "Art. 1531", "slug": "art-1531", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_732079335\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2144\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_732079335\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_225665129\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2143\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_225665129\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Conducerea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> revine în exclusivitate\ndirectoratului, care <span class=SpellE>îndepline&#351;te</span> actele\nnecesare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> utile pentru realizarea obiectului\nde activitate al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, cu <span\nclass=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> celor rezervate de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>lege</i> în sarcina consiliului de supraveghere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\na adun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1892597747\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2142\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1892597747\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Directoratul <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\nexercit&#259; <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;iile</span> sub controlul\nconsiliului de supraveghere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1751457273\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2141\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1751457273\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Directoratul este format din unul sau mai <span\nclass=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span> membri, num&#259;rul acestora fiind totdeauna\nimpar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1151629574\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2140\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1151629574\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Când este un singur membru, acesta poart&#259; denumirea\nde director general unic. În acest caz, <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nart. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>137 alin. (3)</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1085325505\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2139\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1085325505\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În cazul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> ale c&#259;ror <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ii</span>\nfinanciare anuale fac obiectul unei <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ii</span>\nlegale de auditare, directoratul este format din cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\n3 membri.</span></p>"}